Actions

GetIGMPEvents

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPEvents
This action gets the IGMP events that have occurred on the network.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
igmpEvents IGMPEventInfo[] no The list of IGMP events that have occured.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPEventsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPEvents"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "igmpEvents": [
      {
        "clientIPAddress": "192.168.1.101",
        "groupIPAddress": "192.168.1.101",
        "event": "JoinedGroup",
        "timestamp": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z"
      }
    ]
  }
}

GetIGMPSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPSettings
This action gets the current IGMP settings for multicast group management on the network.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
queryInterval int no The time interval (seconds) for IGMP group membership queries.
isFastLeaveEnabled bool no Whether fast-leave is enabled on the network.
maxGroupNumber int no The maximum IGMP multicast group number allowed.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPSettingsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetIGMPSettings"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "queryInterval": 120,
    "isFastLeaveEnabled": true,
    "maxGroupNumber": 256
  }
}

GetSQMInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetSQMInfo
This action gets information about the SQM configuration and status of a router.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sqmSettings SQMSettings yes The SQM settings retrieved from the cloud configuration. This parameter will be omitted if the device has never retrieved a cloud configuration.
lastCloudConfigurationTime DateTime yes The last time the device configuration was retrieved from the cloud. This parameter will be omitted if the device has never retrieved a cloud configuration.
lastHistoricalUploadTime DateTime yes The last time historical data was uploaded to the cloud. This parameter will be omitted if the device has never uploaded historical data.
lastFirmwareUpdateTime DateTime yes The last time the device firmware was updated. This parameter will be omitted if the device has never updated firmware.
provisioningInfo ProvisioningInfo yes The provisioning information for the the router. This parameter will be present only if the device has a network Id.
selfProvisioningStatus string no The current state of the self provisioning process on the router.
selfProvisioningError string yes The last error that occurred, if any, during the self-provisioning process.
cloudConfigurationStatus string no The current state of the cloud configuration retrieval process on the router.
cloudConfigurationError string yes The last error that occurred, if any, during the cloud configuration retrieval process.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetSQMInfoResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/GetSQMInfo"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "sqmSettings": {
      "selfProvisioningEnabled": true,
      "selfReprovision": true,
      "historicalUploadEnabled": true,
      "historicalUploadInterval": 900,
      "historicalUploadHostName": "sg.data.linksyssmartwifi.com",
      "autoFirmwareUpdateEnabled": true,
      "cloudHostName": "cloud1.linksyssmartwifi.com",
      "xmppHostName": "xmpp.linksyssmartwifi.com",
      "cloudExternalIPAddress": "192.168.1.101"
    },
    "lastCloudConfigurationTime": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z",
    "lastHistoricalUploadTime": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z",
    "lastFirmwareUpdateTime": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z",
    "provisioningInfo": {
      "networkId": "network-123456@ciscoconnectcloud.com",
      "isSelfProvisioned": true,
      "userSetNetworkOwner": true
    },
    "selfProvisioningStatus": "stopped",
    "cloudConfigurationStatus": "running",
    "cloudConfigurationError": "ErrorCloudUnavailable"
  }
}

SetIGMPSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/SetIGMPSettings
This action sets the IGMP settings for multicast group management on the network.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
isFastLeaveEnabled bool no Whether fast-leave is enabled on the network.

Output Parameters

This action does not have any output parameters.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/SetIGMPSettingsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDeviceNotInMasterMode This action cannot be executed on a mesh router that is not in Master mode.

Structures

IGMPEventInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/IGMPEventInfo
Information describing an IGMP event.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
clientIPAddress IPAddress no The IP address of the multicast client associated with the event.
groupIPAddress IPAddress no The IP address of the multicast group associated with the event.
event IGMPEvent no The event that occured.
timestamp DateTime no The time of the event.

MulticastClient

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/MulticastClient
Information describing a client member of a multicast group.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
clientMACAddress MACAddress no The MAC address of the multicast client.
clientIPAddress IPAddress no The IP address of the multicast client.
membershipDuration int no The time duration, in seconds, that the client has been a member of the multicast group.

MulticastGroup

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/MulticastGroup
Information describing a multicast group on the network.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
groupIPAddress IPAddress no The IP address of the multicast group.
groupMembers MulticastClient[] no A list of members of the multicast group.

ProvisioningInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/ProvisioningInfo
This service provides access to SQM related settings and information stored in the router's internal state. Information about the provisioning status of the device.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
networkId string no The device network Id.
isSelfProvisioned bool no Whether the device has been self-provisioned.
userSetNetworkOwner bool no Whether the network owner has been set by a user during UI setup.

SQMSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/SQMSettings
The SQM settings for a router.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
selfProvisioningEnabled bool no Whether self provisioning is enabled on the router.
selfReprovision bool no Whether the device should reprovision itself.
historicalUploadEnabled bool no Whether historical data uploading is enabled.
historicalUploadInterval int no The interval, in seconds, at which the historical data is uploaded.
historicalUploadHostName string no The historical upload hostname.
autoFirmwareUpdateEnabled bool no Whether auto firmware update is enabled.
cloudHostName string no The cloud hostname.
xmppHostName string no The xmpp hostname.
cloudExternalIPAddress IPAddress no The cloud external IP address of the device.

Enumerations

IGMPEvent

http://linksys.com/jnap/sqm/IGMPEvent
The IGMP events that can occur on a network.

Enumeration Values

Value Description
JoinedGroup A client joined a multicast group.
LeftGroup A client left a multicast group.
AgedFromGroup A client aged from a multicast group.
